Notice No. 02-07

        January 7, 2002


        TO:             All Exchange Members and Member Firms


        FROM:           J. Robert Collins, Jr., President


        RE:             Delisting of FTSE Eurotop 300

 Futures Contract


        Please be advised that the Exchange has determined to delist the

FTSE Eurotop 300

 Futures contract.  The delisting shall become effective on

Wednesday, January 9, 2002.


        If you have any questions concerning this change, please contact Jay

Gottlieb, Research Department, at (212) 299-2607.
